quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,Hanpety hoye dorney waly ghoron ki qasam
  100,2,Phir taap maar ker aag jharnay walon ki qasam
  100,3,Phir subha kay waqat dhawa bolney walon ki qasam
  100,4,Pus uss waqat gard-o-ghubar uraty hein
  100,5,Phir ussi kay sath fojon kay darmiyan ghos jaty hein
  100,6,Yaqeenan insan apnay rab ka bara nashukra hy
  100,7,Aur yaqeenan who khud bhi issi per gawah hai
  100,8,Yeh maal ki muhabbat mein bhi bara sakht hai
  100,9,Kiya issay who waqat maloom nahi jabb qabron mein jo kuch hy nikal liya jaey ga
  100,10,Aur seenon ki poshida batein zahir kerdi jaeingi
  100,11,Be-shak inka rab uss din unkay haal say poora ba-khabar hoga